These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, cricket
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, mechanic
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, pall-mall
City: london, liverpool
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daffodil, orchid
There are 2 different favourite colors: orange, red
1. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
2. the mechanic is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person who growsdaffodil is the person traveling to liverpool##1
5. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far left##1
6. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Beverage      | fanta     | cola       |
| Sport         | climbing   | cricket     |
| Job           | fisherman | mechanic   |
| Cigar   | pall-mall   | baccarat  |
| City   | liverpool | london |
| Flower           | daffodil      | orchid     |
| Color     | red    | orange   |

