.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: western, horror
There 2 different types of food: zucchini, cranberry
City: paris, miami
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, r&b
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, badminton
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, oliveros
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, van
1. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
2. the oliveros-smoker is the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the fan of indie##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far right##1
5. the person watching western movies is the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Movie-Genre      | western    | horror |
| Food         | cranberry        | zucchini  |
| City           | paris | miami  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b            | indie    |
| Sport   | skateboarding     | badminton   |
| Cigar           | siglo         | oliveros    |
| Transport     | tram           | van      |

